{
  "stem": "2684.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not many people went back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then came American, who wanted to go to America, which was a bit difficult even then.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the Hungarians never came, because Hungary was a very-- first of all, it was a collaborator country.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So nobody liked the Hungarians-- neither the Jews, nor the Yugoslavs, nor the Czechs, nor the Polish people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Hungarians are a very talented nation, but is not very liked by anybody.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I got freed on the 29th of April, and we got the transport somewhere in September.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was in Dachau as a free man till about three or four months.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In these three or four months, we went to Munich, to Munchen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I played my first football game.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Americans organized a football match with another place which called Feldafing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we knew that Feldafing was a girl, a lady lagers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were very anxious to get to Feldafing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when we got to Feldafing we realized that Feldafing was-- I don't know what sort of a lager, but it was on a lakeside, where the other side of the lake was Hitler's holiday resort.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If you read about it, that Hitler [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] keep some treasure in the lakes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was the lakes which was the side of Feldafing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Feldafing was not very far from Garmisch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And Garmisch, even today, is one of the most expensive holiday resorts in Germany-- Garmisch-Partenkirchen they call it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to Feldafing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Americans took us by jeeps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went, and we played against a Feldafing team.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where they organized, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All I know the game consisted of 22 walking zombies, because we were still zombies.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we kicked, and that was the first football game.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
